            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <Card>
        Entenda os problemas ambientais relacionados às contaminações e as
        possibilidades de ocupação de seu terreno com a <span class="accent"
          >Civilsolo Ambiental</span
        >! Entre em contato para esclarecer suas dúvidas!
      </Card>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>

<style>
  .full__background {
    background-color: #e5edd1;
    padding-block: 1rem;
  }
  .row {
    display: flex;
  }
  .download__file__text {
    margin: 0;
    padding-right: 1rem;
    width: 60%;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .file__link {
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    width: 40%;
    text-decoration-color: var(--content-text-color);
  }
  .file__link p {
    margin: 1rem 0 0 0;
  }
  .file__cover {
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;

    transition: 0.4s transform cubic-bezier(0.155, 1.105, 0.295, 1.12),
      0.4s box-shadow,
      0.4s -webkit-transform cubic-bezier(0.155, 1.105, 0.295, 1.12);
    transform: translate3d(0, 1px, 0), rotate(-90deg);
  }

  .row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .file__description__container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .icon__container {
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
    margin-left: 0.4rem;
  }
  .donwload__icon {
    fill: var(--content-text-color);
  }

  .file__link:hover .file__cover {
    box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.23), 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19);
    transform: translate3d(0, -1px, 0) rotate(4deg) scale(1.1);
  }
  .file__link:hover {
    text-decoration-color: var(--sixth-color);
  }
  .file__link:hover .file__description {
    color: var(--sixth-color);
  }
  .file__link:hover .donwload__icon {
    fill: var(--sixth-color);
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .row {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .download__file__text {
      width: 100%;
      padding-bottom: 1.4rem;
    }
    .file__link {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .icon__container {
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    .file__link:hover .file__cover {
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.23),
        0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19);
      transform: translate3d(0, -1px, 0);
    }
  }
</style>
